445
00:29:27,080 --> 00:29:27,800
If so, I'll leave.

446
00:29:35,170 --> 00:29:37,360
Can you walk with your injured leg?

447
00:29:41,071 --> 00:29:43,600
To be honest, it wouldn't be so bad

448
00:29:43,800 --> 00:29:45,019
