469
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:43,520
I wanted to tell you

470
00:30:44,690 --> 00:30:46,170
that I...

471
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:07,906
♪Spinning through my heart,
my dreams, the endless Jianghu♪

472
